      "writtenOn": "2019-08-13T19:29:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, you\u0027ve guessed correctly (see next patch). Since, like Vulkan, Dawn has a single Texture (aka VkImage) object for textures and render targets, a lot of this code was duplicated in the Make function for TRT. I found it cleaner to do it this way.",
      "parentUuid": "6cdfd48c_58b9834c",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 71,
        "startChar": 4,
